This folder is your Archive.

When you type "process my inbox," your Archivist moves files from Team Inbox into here,
organized by year and month (Archive/2026/04/, Archive/2026/05/, and so on).

Your originals are safe here and browseable in Finder or File Explorer at any time.
The Archivist also records every file in a searchable database so you can find anything
later just by asking.

You do not need to manage this folder yourself.
